      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="44562883">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Lily_D/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2003223-8.jpg" alt="做人要呆萌" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44562883/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44562883/" class="">第6页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Lily_D/" class=" " title="做人要呆萌">做人要呆萌</a>
                (NO DO NO DIE)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44562883">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">生命阅历无疑已改变了我对法律的理解，而不变的是那些已经经久确立且仍能与时俱进的法律思想原则。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-04 11:49</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote>生命阅历无疑已改变了我对法律的理解，而不变的是那些已经经久确立且仍能与时俱进的法律思想原则。</blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







